description:
Welcome to the Mortal Realms! If you have a Skaven Paint Set, then this video is for you! Join Ollie as he guides you through painting your scurrying Clanrats using the paints in your set.

Paints included in the set:
Base:
Khorne Red
Leadbelcher
Rakarth Flesh
Steel Legion Drab

Shade:
Agrax Earthshade

Technical: 
Astrogranite

If you're new to painting, our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started.
